  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uplifting Economy of Farmers in 5 Divisions of Ampara District</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Objective #1: To increase knowledge and skills and functionality of 17 farmers organizations in Ampara district. 

Objective #2:  To improve the knowledge and skills of up to 2,210 farmers in farming techniques and crop management in the 5 divisions in Ampara.
 
Objective #3:  To provide agricultural infrastructure, inputs and create linkage with financial institutes to obtain credit through 17 farmer organizations in the 5 divisions of Ampara.

Objective #4:  To increase the number of market opportunities in order to sell farmers&#x2019; agriculture products for a higher price.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to increase household income for more than 2,000 farmers through improved skills and knowledge in agricultural cultivation and production, as well as strengthened organizational capacity amongst local farmers.</narrative>
  </description>
